<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D12.8820.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a01"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:jhead>新菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>經一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a02"/><cb:div><p xml:id="pD12p0001a0201"><note n="0001001" resp="NCLRareBook" place="foot text" type="orig">國圖按：按：此經舊藏經未錄，大正藏係據英倫敦煌本斯坦因136號、622號排印。以館藏此卷校之，大異；捨略有訛脫外，顯較大正所錄兩本優勝。（ 經文對照：大正藏第八十五卷疑似部，號2917A、2917B，頁1462。）</note>新菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>經<g ref="#CB14426"/>諸眾生大小每日念阿<g ref="#CB12752"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a03"/>佛一百口今載大熟湏人万<note n="0001a0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">万【CB】，〃【國圖】</note><app n="0001a0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA">万</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">〃</rdg></app>億湏牛万
<lb ed="D" n="0001a04"/><note n="0001a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">万【CB】，〃【國圖】</note><app n="0001a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA">万</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">〃</rdg></app>頭勸諸眾生斷<g ref="#CB08891"/>脩善禾丘無人
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D12.8820.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/><note n="0002a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add"><g ref="#CB15756"/>【CB】，<unclear></unclear>【國圖】</note><app n="0002a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><g ref="#CB15756"/></lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>苅苐一病死苐二卆死苐三赤眼死
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/>苐四腫病死苐五產生死苐六患腹。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/><p xml:id="pD12p0002a0301">有眼眾生冩一本免一身冩兩本免一
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/>門冩三本免一村若不信者即滅門。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/><p xml:id="pD12p0002a0501">此經<g ref="#CB30130"/>西亰州正月二日盛中時雷<note n="0002a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">鳴【CB】，明【國圖】</note><app n="0002a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">鳴</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">明</rdg></app>雨
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/>聲有一石下大如<g ref="#CB08128"/>遂兩片即見此經
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/>報諸眾生今載饒患。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="1"><cb:jhead>新菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>經一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>